cable_repair.body:
{{greeting}}

Thanks for your enquiry.

For a cable/spring repair, please send:

* photos from inside and outside;
* close-ups of the cable/drum area on both sides;
* whether the door is manual or electric;
* whether the door is fully closed and secure;
* your postcode;
* whether you would like a repair visit/quote.

We usually arrange quotes on {{quote_day}}s, but if the door is insecure or stuck open, please let us know as urgent.

Kind regards,

{{business_name}}

